<Content>Be Warned: Worst Hospitality Ever! This hotel does not deserve even one star! A waste of money, at $600 a night for a suite, this hotel was a joke! The toilet ran all night, dirty carpet and upholstery, torn bedspreads, broken mirrors, coffee pots that don't work, the spa was not heated, the pool was dirty, no phone books or room service menus in the room, no microwave, empty entertainment center, rude and arrogant ownership and management as well as dissatisifed employees. The one touch service button on the phone was never answered after letting it ring in excess of 10 times. In the 25+ years I have been traveling for business and pleasure, this was the worst hospitality I have ever experienced! This is definitely not a place to bring your business!February, 2007 
