<Content>Excellent Value We stayed here on a quick visit from the West Coast for my father in laws birthday. Although this hotel is no longer a Radisson, they seem intent on keeping up a high standard. Wonderfully large and clean rooms. Warm and friendly staff. Nice touches such as beach towels by the pool and small towels and water in the fitness room. We didn't eat there so can't comment on the restaurant. This will definitely be our place to stay when we visit Miami again... great value. 
