<Content>Horrible service, Great room Room was great. Very large with king bed, sitting area and a table with two chairs. Pretty good location but the service was horrible! I was there for two nights but met up with a co-worker who arrive a few days before me. He told me about his A/C smoking and he could not get anyone to answer at the front desk, restraunt, the EMERGENCY button on the phone or any other number. That night I am getting ready for bed and notice no clock...so I call the front desk...no answer. I notice it has speak so I let it ring...for 10 min while gettng ready, no answer. Call the restraunt and any other button on the phone and still no answer so I decide to call the emegency number. Let it ring 10 times and no answer. So I give up and use my phone for the alarm clock. The next night I expect the same thing but I get a person to answer and order a wake up call, he confirms the time, and I go to sleep....next morning I wake up late, no wake up call. Horrible service but the room is nice. 
