<Content>A relaxing and friendly hotel Unfortunate circumstances caused me to stay here, as my father was admitted to the Baptist Hospital next door. After spending all day at the hospital I found enormous pleasure in returning to the hotel. All of the staff had a welcoming smile and showed genuine warmth. The room was great, good aircon, comfortable beds and sofa. There is a good pool, which I only got to use once and two tennis courts. Food, drink and service were all our a high quality. Recommended. 
